，我也不會感到很驚訝。」<br />\n<br />\n任職港大公共衛生學院院長及臨牀教授的福田敬二在2016年加入港大，來港前曾擔任世衛多個要職，包括世衛大流行流感總幹事特別顧問、衛生安全助理總幹事等，亦曾在美國疾控中心任職，多年來應付過SARS、MERS、伊波拉病毒等多場疫症。本港今年初爆發新冠病毒疫情，福田敬二獲特首林鄭月娥委任加入4人專家顧問團，他在2月底已預計疫情相當可能演變成全球大流行，又多次讚揚港府及港人抗疫做得好。<br />\n<br />\n港大醫學院近期已流失多名教授，微生物學系3名教授於本學年先後離職，包括劉嘉珮、胡釗逸及黃世賢。<br />\n<br />\n明報記者<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20201007/s00002/1602009247833/%E6%8A%97%E7%96%AB%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6%E7%A6%8F%E7%94%B0%E6%95%AC%E4%BA%8C%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%A7%E7%BA%8C%E7%B4%84-%E5%8E%9F%E7%8D%B2%E5%AD%B8%E8%A1%93%E5%AF%A9%E6%89%B9%E6%9C%83%E9%80%9A%E9%81%8E-%E6%B6%88%E6%81%AF-%E5%BC%B5%E7%BF%94%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201007%2Fs00002%2F1602009247833%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E6%2595%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25BF%2594%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA&d=lMjb5htdGhqouCxjtFETmT%2BQayrLlxBj8%2BPX1Ib8Zww%3D&h=c4c3d469\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20201007%2Fs00002%2F1602009247833%2F%25E6%258A%2597%25E7%2596%25AB%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E7%25A6%258F%25E7%2594%25B0%25E6%2595%25AC%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25BA%258C%25E7%25B4%2584-%25E5%258E%259F%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E8%25A1%2593%25E5%25AF%25A9%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2580%259A%25E9%2581%258E-%25E6%25B6%2588%25E6%2581%25AF-%25E5%25BC%25B5%25E7%25BF%2594%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA&h=bc00bc00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://new